This_sync_version_may_multiply_each_scri.message:
Unlike the 'Legacy' sync version this one synchronizes your scripts by reference to a unique ID that is created when a script is installed!

This means if you installed a script at multiple Tampermonkey instances by either another sync method or a normal script installation then this script will appear multiple times after the next sync iteration has finished.

The only way to recover is to manually remove each doubled script entry!
